

ls --> For list the files
cd --> Change Directory
pwd --> Preview Working Directory
mkdir --> Make Directory
touch --> to create empty files and updating the timestamps of existing files.
cat > FileName  --> To write Something in a file  || To exit Press (Ctrl + d)  || If we again run this command and write something then that will be overriden
cat >> FileName --> To Write something in the existing file in next line
cat filename --> To Display the content of the file
